<div id='imageData' data-json='{"infobox":{"file":"2481856-box_harvest.png","path":"8\/87790\/","mime":"image\/png","sizes":"square_small,square_tiny,square_medium,scale_tiny,scale_small,square_mini,square_avatar,scale_medium,screen_medium,scale_large,scale_avatar,scale_super,screen_kubrick","caption":"WIN8 box art (cropped)"},"background":[]}' />
==Overview== The Harvest is a touch based action RPG first released on Windows Phone on October 15, 2010. An updated version titled The Harvest HD is set to be released for Windows 8 on October 26, 2012.

